import React from 'react'
import {Container, Button, Row, Col} from "react-bootstrap"

export default function Botones() {
    return (
        <Container style={{display: "flex", alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center"}}>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <Button style={{ margin: "5px"}}>
                        Siguiente
                    </Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                   <Button style={{ margin: "5px"}}>
                       Anterior
                   </Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>          
        </Container>
    )
}
